{"tid":1749780,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"就算你選區只有一個藍候選人，唔該你都出黎投票","createTime":"2019-11-24T06:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T06:47:38.000Z","uid":82312,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"93416a8bb191c2f413560e7a6aa81da111343f94","tid":1749780,"uid":82312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:20:27.000Z","msg":"今次選舉實際影響其實唔大<br />\n但就係6月到依家唯一一次有好大公信力嘅投票<br />\n一人一票係一個變相嘅公投<br />\n而每一票都係有晒數字嘅記錄，<br />\n不論係投黃，藍定白票，係好有意義<br />\n不分黃藍，200萬人又係我地講，藍絲又話自己係沉默大多數<br />\n<br />\n大家只要有晒咁多區數字，<br />\n基本上就可以好確實咁知道依家不滿政府嘅人實實在在有幾多<br />\n中央，外國，都自己中心有<br />\n冇錯雖然佢地會繼續扮見唔到，<br />\n但呢個係後話<br />\n<br />\n所以就算係只有一個候選人，都要出黎投白票<br />\n蛇齋餅粽冇錯都仲係有，<br />\n但對今次呢個投票人數黎講<br />\n今次選舉依然好有公信力<br />\n你信又好唔信又好，投左先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11023520621a50e66da864290e3d383899ce55bd","tid":1749780,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:32:11.000Z","msg":"公乜撚嘢信力 Cls<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nhedf0j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNhedf0j.png&h=15eee1b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nhK4661.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnhK4661.png&h=93765cf8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"160a6891bfc2cd449d17374ae263fa54ac32943d","tid":1749780,"uid":973,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:47:38.000Z","msg":"無記錯呢屆區區都有2位以上<br />\n無人自動當選<br />\n所以不投建制派"}]}